trans-unit.source: Specifies the standard keys on a console.
trans-unit.target: Anger standard nycklarna på en konsol.

trans-unit.source: The ConsoleKey enumeration is typically used in the nfo structure, which is returned by the <xref:System.Console.ReadKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to indicate which key on the console has been pressed.
trans-unit.target: Uppräkningen ConsoleKey används vanligtvis i nfo-struktur som returneras av den <xref:System.Console.ReadKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metod för att ange vilka tangent på konsolen har tryckts.</xref:System.Console.ReadKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
